OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FJersey needs to develop a long-term
OL,8,Fstrategy to better engage with younger
OL,9,Fvoters, according to a political
OL,10,Fadvertising expert.
OL,12,FDr Chris Pich, Associate Professor of
OL,13,FMarketing at the University of
OL,14,FNottingham, says democracy is "dusted
OL,15,Foff every four years" for election
OL,16,Fcampaigns in Jersey, with not enough
OL,17,Fdone to create lasting change in young
OL,18,Fislanders' attitudes to local politics
OL,19,Fin the in-between.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
