OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FHis comments come after ITV News found
OL,8,Frecent hustings events attracted next
OL,9,Fto no young voters.
OL,11,FDr Pich has a specific interest in the
OL,12,FChannel Islands, having carried out
OL,13,Fresearch alongside organisations in
OL,14,Fboth Jersey and Guernsey to better
OL,15,Funderstand voter engagement.
OL,17,FIn 2023, he teamed up with the States
OL,18,FGreffe to produce a major report
OL,19,Flooking at the barriers to engagement
OL,20,Fwith politics in Jersey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FThe review made several key
OL,8,Frecommendations:
OL,10,F1. Better civic education
OL,12,FDr Pich explains: "Education is the
OL,13,Fkey driver to long-term sustained
OL,14,Fengagement.
OL,16,F"Vote.je and the States Assembly
OL,17,Freally need to think about developing
OL,18,Fa long-term strategy beyond the
OL,19,Felection - not just roll out these
OL,20,Fgreat tactics every four years."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FHe hopes his team has found a
OL,8,Fsolution, however - his work in Jersey
OL,9,Finvolved piloting an educational
OL,10,Fproject for young voters at Highlands
OL,11,FCollege earlier this year.
OL,13,FDr Pich says: "We're creating content
OL,14,Fthat we hope to then roll out in
OL,15,Fschools across Jersey to basically
OL,16,Faddress those key issues - why people
OL,17,Fshould vote, why it makes a
OL,18,Fdifference, distinction between
OL,19,Fdifferent politicians.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,F"We've created a whole set of
OL,8,Fresources and the plan is, after the
OL,9,Felection, we roll that out to all
OL,10,Fschools to have those targeted
OL,11,Fprogrammes to address those knowledge
OL,12,Fgaps."
OL,14,F2. More creative ways to engage young
OL,15,Fvoters
OL,17,FDr Pich says he acknowledges the
OL,18,Fdifficulties of Jersey's specific
OL,19,Fpolitical context, with independent
OL,20,Fpoliticians having to stand out
OL,21,Famongst a crowd of 92 candidates.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FHowever, he adds that whilst hustings
OL,8,Fand door-knocking have their place
OL,9,Fwithin an election campaign, "we need
OL,10,Fto bring in new creative campaign
OL,11,Ftactics as well to reach different
OL,12,Ftarget markets, different voter
OL,13,Fgroups".
OL,15,FWhen he spoke with young voters in
OL,16,FJersey earlier this year, they
OL,17,Fdescribed events such as traditional
OL,18,Fcandidate fairs as "intimidating",
OL,19,Fsaying they wanted to see more
OL,20,F"creative" tactics.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FDr Pich adds: "If you think about
OL,8,FGuernsey's election last year, they
OL,9,Fhad some cracking creative
OL,10,Felectioneering tactics.
OL,12,F"They had an open mic night where
OL,13,Fcandidates did a bit of comedy but
OL,14,Falso linked it to their political
OL,15,Fbeliefs, they had a battle bike which
OL,16,Fappealed to young voters, and a 'meet
OL,17,Fthe candidates' event at the Bathing
OL,18,FPools."
OL,20,F3. Politicians who engage and identify
OL,21,Fwith the electorate
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FDr Pich says: "We've seen that not
OL,8,Fonly in Jersey but in Guernsey, seeing
OL,9,Fis believing, because they want to see
OL,10,Fyoung people represented in the States.
OL,12,F"They want to vote for younger people
OL,13,Fand say 'that person understands me'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,F"That's one of the biggest barriers
OL,8,Fyoung people have when it comes to
OL,9,Fvoting, they just see 'men in suits' -
OL,10,Fthat's the phrase I often hear - and
OL,11,Fthey want to look beyond that and find
OL,12,Fsomebody they feel they can engage
OL,13,Fwith, and that person is authentic and
OL,14,Fbelievable."
OL,16,F4. A long-term strategy lasting beyond
OL,17,Felection years
OL,19,FThe need for an overriding plan that
OL,20,Flasts after this year's election is Dr
OL,21,FPich's key message.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FHe explains: "There needs to be a long-
OL,8,Fterm strategy developed to focus on
OL,9,F(the problem of political engagement).
OL,11,F"It needs to be fully resourced - not
OL,12,Fjust something that's dusted off every
OL,13,Ffour years. It has to be a change of
OL,14,Fculture within Jersey - it needs to be
OL,15,Fa collective approach."
OL,26,@qD@ApmqD@epn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779217874
OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FHe adds that the uniqueness of the
OL,8,FChannel Islands - with independent
OL,9,Fpolitical systems - creates
OL,10,Fopportunities to trial new ways of
OL,11,Fimproving engagement and
OL,12,Frepresentation in politics.
OL,14,FHowever, meaningful cultural change
OL,15,Frequires consistent engagement with
OL,16,Fyoung people before election campaigns
OL,17,Fbegin - and long after they end.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
