OL,3,C'They just see men in suits':
OL,4,CPolitical expert on Jersey's young
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,8,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,9,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,10,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,11,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,12,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,13,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,14,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,15,FThursday...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/12
